Alpha Brands CORE Equity


The Alpha Brands CORE Equity strategy is our flagship long-only portfolio. A U.S. Large Cap focused “best of the best” portfolio of the most relevant and powerful Brands. Targets 35-40 Iconic Brands, rebalanced quarterly. The final portfolio names are a sub-segment of the Alpha Brands Consumer Spending Index, a proprietary Index created by Accuvest. The Index constituents are the Top 200 most relevant brands chosen every December by the Accuvest Investment Committee.


Strategic


PRIMARILY U.S DOMICILED


