PDF



Alpha Brands Dynamic Equity


The Alpha Brands DYNAMIC Equity strategy uses a portion of the CORE Brands portfolio plus allows the Investment Committee (IC) more latitude to invest in other Iconic Brands from within the 200 universe. The IC also has flexibility to hold up to 40% in cash or fixed income if equity markets have deteriorated sufficiently to warrant a move to the sidelines.


