Accuvest Global Advisors Partners with First Trust to Launch a New International Strategy Featuring AlphaDEX® Country ETFs

		  Accuvest International Opportunities - Featuring AlphaDEX® ETFs Will Pair Top-Down Country Selection with Bottom-Up Stock Selection
		

May 17, 2012, 13:10 ET
		  		  					
						 from   Accuvest Global Advisors 











 
















































 

 




















 


WALNUT CREEK, Calif., May 17, 2012 /PRNewswire/ -- Accuvest Global Advisors ("Accuvest"), a leading investment manager of global/international equity strategies, today announced that they will launch a new model strategy that will combine Accuvest's top-down country selection with First Trust Advisors AlphaDEX® methodology.  
The new strategy, branded Accuvest International Opportunities – Featuring AlphaDEX® ETFs, will initially be offered on select UMA platforms.  David Garff, President of Accuvest Global Advisors said, "We are thrilled about our new partnership with First Trust.  Both of our firms use a quantitative methodology to access country markets, ours from a country level and theirs on a company level.  Together, our methodologies will offer investors access to the most attractive companies within the most attractive countries."
Accuvest has been running their country ranking model over the last 7 years for a global client base as well as both domestic and international investment companies.  Their strategies have consistently featured single-country ETFs which has differentiated them from the majority of global managers.  Andy Subramanian, Senior Vice President of First Trust said, "It is rare to find a manager like Accuvest that views the world from the top-down.  Their methodology and track record for selecting countries makes them an ideal model manager of AlphaDEX® ETFs.  This new strategy meets the need for international diversification that is not constrained by traditional market cap indexing."
About Accuvest Global AdvisorsAccuvest Global Advisors is headquartered in Walnut Creek, CA. Founded in 2005, Accuvest serves as investment adviser to a variety of global individual and institutional investor accounts, such as families, foundations, institutional investors, private funds, and financial intermediaries. www.accuvest.com
About First Trust Advisors L.P.First Trust is headquartered in Wheaton, Il. Established in 1991, First Trust offers investment services including asset management, financial advisory services, and municipal underwriting to a variety of clients.  They also offer an array of investment vehicles, including UITs, ETFs, ETNs, closed-end funds, mutual funds, annuities, separate managed accounts, and structured products. www.ftportfolios.com
Contact: David AllenAccuvest Global Advisors925-930-2882david.allen@accuvest.com
